      "text": "## Problem\n\nAfter deploying a new workspace and submitting a request to the `senior-coder` agent via `exactl`, the request processing fails with `plan.validation.failed`. This occurs despite the daemon starting successfully and the agent apparently completing its execution.\n\n## Reproduction Steps\n\n```bash\n# 1. deploy workspace (simulated)\n./scripts/deploy_workspace.sh ~/Exaix\n\n# 2. Configure and start daemon\ncp exa.config.sample.toml exa.config.toml\nexactl daemon start\n\n# 3. Create test portal\ncat >> ~/Exaix/exa.config.toml << EOF\n[[portals]]\nalias = \"TestApp\"\ntarget_path = \"/tmp/test-portal\"\nEOF\n\nmkdir -p /tmp/test-portal/src\ncd /tmp/test-portal\ngit init\necho \"# Test App\" > README.md\necho \"export const version = '1.0';\" > src/index.ts\ngit add . && git commit -m \"Initial commit\"",
